race.comment: JUST IN CASEY (4) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 3 lengths (37.31) at this track. Rates on top again. MY DEAR FRIEND (3) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (37.51) at this track over 650m. Expected to be in this for a long way. CHARENTE JEWEL (5) shapes well after a useful run last time, finishing third in a Restricted WIN H at this track in 37.51. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. BLUE TROMBONE (1) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start. Something for the Multiples: KING OF SNAKE (7)

runners.name: Thank You Brian
